  "body": "### What is wrong?\r\nSync with the spec: https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/blob/master/specs/core/0_beacon-chain.md#helper-functions\r\n- [x] `def get_active_validator_indices(validators)`\r\n- [x] `def shuffle(values: List[Any], seed: Hash32) -> List[Any]`\r\n- [x] `def split(seq: List[Any], split_count: int) -> List[Any]`\r\n- [x] `def clamp(minval: int, maxval: int, x: int) -> int`\r\n- [x] `def get_new_shuffling(seed: Hash32, validators: List[ValidatorRecord],  crosslinking_start_shard: int) -> List[List[ShardAndCommittee]]`\r\n- [x] `def get_block_hash(state: BeaconState, current_block: BeaconBlock, slot: int) -> Hash32`\r\n- [x] `def get_beacon_proposer(state:BeaconState, slot: int) -> ValidatorRecord`\r\n- [x] `def add_validator_set_change_record(state: BeaconState, index: int, pubkey: int, flag: int) -> None`\r\n- [x] `def int_sqrt(n: int) -> int`\r\n\r\n### How can it be fixed\r\n1. Go through the code and see if anything require updates.\r\n2. Turn on the test (`tests/beacon/test_helpers.py`) or write new tests.",
